name: Cube speed!
description:
CUBE SPEED!

A infinite game of cubes, can you beat your max score?

HOW TO PLAY

Avoid red cubes pressing W/A/S/D or arrow keys

Buy upgrades in the shop with your score

Press ALT+Enter to swith fullscreen (no very compatible)

The used music is Karlson Vibe

If you dont want to donate, it's great if you subscribe to my channel

New update in 2 days
